{"type": "article", "id": 14109, "title": "有记忆力的钢笔", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-28T07:27:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140506KXl20EB9FTgSJkRm.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国品牌 Orée 正在试图全方位占领你的书桌，最近他们推出了这一款有记忆力的钢笔，配有专门的纸张，笔中设置了一个高速微型摄像机，可以跟踪 记录书写轨迹，创建电子版文档，用蓝牙和智能手机连接起来，便可以自动获得书写的内容。另外，这个名为 Stylograph 的笔外观上简约干净，采用磨砂质地的黄铜材料，看上去很是时尚大方。产品将会在下个月正式面市，<a href=\"http://oreeartisans.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141716iUIEta0MwN3bQHsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141717mGHkVxbQ2FChPa9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141717fOa4eBPnuRvwmFsN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59535452\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141717VagCT1OE3fKFzopj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141719GDlCTZIxuvBE9JFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141719zp4aL9lRT0SNrKou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141720t1YGW2Au8ohzv0k4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141721THMeVci4kyorfaGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}